<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{{.Name}} - Email</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.kainonly.com/assets/skeleton.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h3>你好，{{.User}}</h3>
    <p>邮箱验证码为：</p>
    <h4 style="letter-spacing: 4px">{{.Code}}</h4>
    <p>5分钟内有效，逾期后您需要重新获取，切勿将验证码提供给他人</p>
    <small>本邮件由系统自动发送，请勿直接回复！</small>
    <hr>
    <small><em>Copyright © 2023 {{.Year}} {{.Name}}. All rights reserved.</em></small>
</div>
</body>
</html>

